<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>xìng qǐ ba wǒ de xīn 迦南9</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wēi wēi de gāo shān, máng máng de hǎi yáng, wǒ zhàn zài gāo shān gé hǎi guān wàng.
 jī dū de jīng bīng bēn fù zhàn chǎng, tā men zhèng bǎ fú yīn liè huǒ diǎn wàng.
 lí kāi qīn rén, bèi jǐng lí xiāng, shōu gē zhuāng mù yǎng qún yáng,
 wǒ de xīn zhōng, rè xuè zài liú tǎng, zài zhè yǒu xiàn nián rì, wǒ gāi zěn me yàng?
 xìng qǐ ba! wǒ de xīn! xìng qǐ ba mò hòu de rén!
 xǔ duō shǐ mìng hé tuō fù, zài wǒ men zhè yī dài jiān shàng.
 zǒu guò jiān nán de hēi yè, yíng zhe lí míng de shǔ guāng,
 tiān nán de běi líng bāo xiāng yīng hū huàn, yī tóng bēn shàng zhàn chǎng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>9</hymn_number>
</song>